episodes.title: Born Again
episodes.plot: Three months after Jacs death, new arrival Joan Ferguson makes an enemy of Franky, while Bea discovers a new purpose.

episodes.title: Whatever It Takes
episodes.plot: Bea attempts to get revenge on Brayden by goading Harry into an act of violence, whilst Franky's determination to maintain power pushes her to extreme lengths.

episodes.title: Boys in the Yard
episodes.plot: Following the failure of Harry to avenge their daughter's death, Bea hatches a daring plot to lure Brayden Holt to the jail.

episodes.title: The Danger Within
episodes.plot: Bea faces down an assassination attempt from the Holt clan. While new inmates enter the compound.

episodes.title: Twist the Knife
episodes.plot: Bea discovers Simmo has a weakness she can exploit for her own ends. Meanwhile Fletch and Will face off in a confrontation that will end their friendship for good.

episodes.title: The Pink Dragon
episodes.plot: Simmo's attempt to kill Bea ends in tragedy, while Liz faces her greatest dilemma: to snitch or not to snitch.

episodes.title: Metamorphosis
episodes.plot: When Ferguson psychologically manipulates Vera she crosses a point of no return whilst Maxine orchestrates a desperate bid to see her spurned lover.

episodes.title: Sins of the Mother
episodes.plot: An isolated and paranoid Franky tries to uncover which inmate is leaking vital information to Ferguson.

episodes.title: The Fixer
episodes.plot: When Ferguson discovers Doreen is the pregnant prisoner, the Governor threatens to have Nash's parole revoked unless she lies about the father. Will is publicly accused of an inappropriate relationship with Bea.

episodes.title: Jail Birds
episodes.plot: Liz struggles to adjust to life on the outside and tries to reconnect with her estranged children. Meanwhile, Derek Channing tries to build his case against Ferguson.

episodes.title: Into the Night
episodes.plot: As Bea and Franky go to war for control of the prison, Bea puts her daring plan in motion. Meanwhile, Fletch is on a downward spiral of self-destructive behaviour as his final day at Wentworth looms.

episodes.title: Fear Her
episodes.plot: The extent of Bea's plan is revealed as she makes the final moves to avenge Debbie's death. Meanwhile Franky realises she is losing the support of the women and is forced to consider a deal.
